question: How should one proceed to stop spreading the fertilizer?
model_answer: You should close the cab by shutting all doors and windows. Then, drive with the first gear in accordance with the desired driving pattern, looking for the marked positions on the steering column. Next, turn on the control panel. Check the settings as described in the manual. Without GEOCONTROL select and activate a parcel number in the parcel registration system. Set the speed of the tractor to the corresponding table given in the Streutabelle. Do not over-dress the tires with closed dosing units. Press the start button simultaneously with the opening of the dosing units. The speed of the tractor (and thus the drive motor) must remain constant during the spreading process. You can adjust the speed by switching to another gear.
